                            <comment id="122859" author="simmonsja" created="Fri, 31 Jul 2015 15:09:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;With the patch from John Hammond for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6835&quot; title=&quot;lfs.c:481: error: implicit declaration of function &amp;#39;futimes&amp;#39;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-6835&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-6835&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; the compiler has strict defense mode for the user land code.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
